%% Diagram: gRPC's four streaming modes over a single HTTP/2 stream
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server

    Note over C,S: Unary
    C->>S: Request
    S-->>C: Response

    Note over C,S: Server streaming
    C->>S: Request
    S-->>C: Response 1
    S-->>C: Response 2
    S-->>C: Response N (END_STREAM)

    Note over C,S: Client streaming
    C->>S: Request 1
    C->>S: Request 2
    C->>S: Request N (END_STREAM)
    S-->>C: Final response

    Note over C,S: Bidirectional
    C->>S: Request 1
    S-->>C: Response 1
    C->>S: Request 2
    S-->>C: Response 2
